Description: Chen cortical atlases for the 'ggseg' ecosystem. Provides
    unified 'ggseg_atlas' objects with 2D polygon geometry for use with
    'ggseg'. Includes both thickness (chenTh) and areal (chenAr)
    parcellations from Chen et al. (2013).
